## 1. Format layout

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ [MAGIC      4B ] "NATT" (0x4E 0x41 0x54 0x54)                  │
│ [VERSION    2B ] uint16 BE — 0x0100 = v1.0                     │
│ [HDR_LEN    4B ] uint32 BE                                     │
│ [HEADER     var] plaintext JSON — identity + KDF meta          │
│ [MAN_LEN    4B ] uint32 BE                                     │
│ [MANIFEST   var] AES-256-GCM(JSON, key, nonce_man)             │
│ [BODY_LEN   8B ] uint64 BE                                     │
│ [BODY       var] AES-256-GCM(tar.zst, key, nonce_body)         │
│ [GCM_TAG    16B] GCM authentication tag over HEADER+MAN+BODY   │
│ [END_MAGIC  4B ] "TTAN"                                        │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 1.1 HEADER plaintext schema
```json
{
  "$nauion": "NATT-v1.0",
  "kind": "ColonyPack",
