## 6. CLI interface

```bash
# Pack
natt-pack --source . --output pack.natt --flavor for-kim
natt-pack --source . --output full.natt --flavor full
natt-pack --source . --output demo.natt --flavor public

# Unpack
natt-unpack pack.natt
natt-unpack pack.natt --target ./restored/

# Validate (dry-run, no extract)
natt-validate pack.natt
# Output:
#   ✅ MAGIC OK
#   ✅ VERSION 1.0
#   ✅ HEADER parsed
#   ✅ GCM auth OK
#   ✅ Manifest decrypted
#   ✅ 1552 files in pack
#   ℹ  colony: natt-os_verANC
#   ℹ  flavor: for-kim
#   ℹ  packed_at: 2026-04-20T21:30:00
```

