## 7. Implementation — 3 Python scripts

| File | Lines est | Dependencies |
|---|---|---|
| `natt-pack.py` | ~300 | `hashlib`, `hmac`, `cryptography` (AES-GCM), `zstandard`, `tarfile`, `json`, `argparse` |
| `natt-unpack.py` | ~250 | same |
| `natt-validate.py` | ~150 | same (no extract step) |

**Critical libs:**
- `cryptography` — Python de-facto crypto lib (not stdlib, but ubiquitous)
- `zstandard` — Facebook zstd Python binding

**Lenh[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] #001 compliance check:** Both libs pure Python/C, khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] Giao The[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] ra network ngoai[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] ✅

**Install:**
```bash
pip install cryptography zstandard
```

